<div class="pa"><div class="i"><img class="im" src="~@img/13220.png"></div><div class="t"><p>失乡骑士头盔</p><br>基于某种理由或罪刑，<br>因此失去故乡的失乡骑士们穿戴的头盔。<br>为保护全身的厚重盔甲。<br><br>深红色的披肩带可能是用于挡风，<br>毕竟边境的风寒冷刺骨。<br>表面盖着深红色布料的骑士头盔</div><div class="t"><p>失地騎士の兜</p><br>全身を覆う重厚な全身鎧<br>何らかの理由、あるいは咎で<br>故郷を失くした失地騎士たちの兜<br><br>えんじ色のストールは、風除けであろうか<br>辺境の風は、身に染みて冷たい<br><br>騎士兜を、えんじ色の長布で覆ったもの</div><div class="t"><p>Banished Knight Helm</p><br>Thick, full set of armor covering the entire body.<br>This helm was worn by knights who, whether by misfortune or misdeed, were forced to abandon their homes.<br><br>Perhaps the deep-red scarf was used to block the winds, for on the outskirts, the winds bite with a stinging fierceness.<br>Knight's helm covered in a long cloth of deep red</div></div>
