<div class="pa"><div class="i"><img class="im" src="~@img/13261.png"></div><div class="t"><p>随从上衣</p><br>侍奉权贵、保护主人的随从们穿戴的上衣。<br><br>制作得颇为优质的旅行服装，<br>为的是不失体面。<br>随从穿戴的上衣</div><div class="t"><p>小姓の服</p><br>貴人に仕え、主を守る小姓たちの服<br><br>従者として恥ずかしいことの無いよう<br>上質に仕立てられた旅装<br><br>小姓の服</div><div class="t"><p>Page Garb</p><br>Garb worn by pages who serve the nobility and are mindful to keep them out of harm's way.<br><br>Traveling wear tailored with exquisite precision, to avoid any undue shame for the page's master.<br>Garb worn by pages</div></div>
