<div class="pa"><div class="i"><img class="im" src="~@img/13520.png"></div><div class="t"><p>火焰主教头盔</p><br>有着头顶火杯的尊容头盔。<br>火焰习武修士们的领导者，<br>主教穿戴的防具。<br><br>据说头顶的火杯原本有放置火种，<br>当虔诚的心到达颠峰时，会冒出滚烫火焰。<br>只是那景象已经难以重现。<br>以年长智者形象制成的火焰主教头盔</div><div class="t"><p>火の司教の兜</p><br>頭盃を乗せた、尊顔の兜<br>火の僧兵たちの指導者たる、司教の装束<br><br>その頭盃には、本来火種が宿り<br>信仰の滾りを大いに噴き上げるという<br>だが、それはもう消えている<br><br>老賢を象った、火の司教の兜</div><div class="t"><p>Fire Prelate Helm</p><br>Helm engraved with a sacred countenance and housing a cauldron.<br>Attire of the Fire Prelates, commanders of the Fire Monks.<br><br>It is said the cauldron perched atop the head was originally furnished with embers, and would surge into flames when the wearer's faith reached its zenith. The fire of this cauldron has since died out, however.<br>Fire Prelate helm sculpted in the image of a sage</div></div>
<div class="pa"><div class="i"><img class="im" src="~@img/13521.png"></div><div class="t"><p>火焰主教铠甲</p><br>搭配鲜红上衣的黑铁制铠甲。<br>火焰习武修士们的领导者，<br>主教穿戴的防具。<br><br>身躯庞大的模样是担下火焰监视者，<br>此一重责大任的象征。<br><br>　将我等形如盘石的模样，牢记心底了。<br>搭配鲜红上衣的火焰主教铠甲</div><div class="t"><p>火の司教の鎧</p><br>赤衣を纏った黒鉄の胴鎧<br>火の僧兵たちの指導者たる、司教の装束<br><br>でっぷりと太ったその姿は<br>火の監視者の任、その重さの象徴である<br>しかと心に刻むがよい。我が姿、重石たるを<br><br>赤衣を纏った、火の司教の胴鎧</div><div class="t"><p>Fire Prelate Armor</p><br>Black iron armor adorned with a red cloth.<br>Attire of the Fire Prelates, commanders of the Fire Monks.<br><br>The weighty frames of the Prelates symbolized the onus of their grave vows as guardians of the flame. "Etch this sight upon thine breast. Of my thunderous gravity."<br>Fire Prelate armor adorned with a red cloth</div></div>
